		<h3>Instructions</h3>
		<p class="title">(Click each step after completing them to keep track!)</p>
		<ol>
		<li>Lay out square section of <strong>Seaweed Wrap</strong></li>
		<li>Cover evenly in <strong>Rice</strong></li>
		<li>Lay strip of <strong>Salmon</strong> down one edge of <strong>Rice</strong> covered <strong>Wrap</strong></li>
		<li>Roll <strong>Wrap</strong> until <em>complete</em>!</li>
		</ol>

